text: Constantin Van Rijckevorsel (born 24 June 1976) is a Belgian equestrian. He competed at the 1996 Summer Olympics, the 2000 Summer Olympics and the 2004 Summer Olympics. ==References== Category:1976 births Category:Living people Category:Belgian male equestrians Category:Olympic equestrians of Belgium Category:Equestrians at the 1996 Summer Olympics Category:Equestrians at the 2000 Summer Olympics Category:Equestrians at the 2004 Summer Olympics Category:People from Uccle
